{"article_id":"lyswScVQTy9SAAC4","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Well , it ' s been discussed .","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"It ' s been debated .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"And now the Trump White House supposedly has a final decision :","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"The Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals program","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that originated under the Obama administration","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"is over .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"There will be a six-month enforcement delay , however .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"Eliana Johnson of Politico has more","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"[ Emphasis mine ] :","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"President Donald Trump has decided to end the Obama-era program","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that grants work permits to undocumented immigrants","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"who arrived in the country as children ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"according to two sources familiar with his thinking .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Senior White House aides huddled Sunday afternoon","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"to discuss the rollout of a decision","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"likely to ignite a political firestorm","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"- and fulfill one of the president ' s core campaign promises .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Trump has wrestled for months with whether to do away with the Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"known as DACA .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"He has faced strong warnings from members of his own party","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"not to scrap the program","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"and struggled with his own misgivings","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"about targeting minors for deportation .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"Conversations with Attorney General Jeff Sessions ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"who argued","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"that Congress","depth":15},{"id":26,"text":"- rather than the executive branch -","depth":15},{"id":27,"text":"is responsible","depth":14},{"id":28,"text":"for writing immigration law ,","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"helped persuade the president to terminate the program ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"the two sources said ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"though White House aides caution","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that - as with everything in the Trump White House -","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"nothing is set in stone","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"until an official announcement has been made .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"In a nod to reservations","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"held by many lawmakers ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"the White House plans to delay the enforcement of the president ' s decision for six months ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"giving Congress a window","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"to act ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"according to one White House official .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"But a senior White House aide said","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"that chief of staff John Kelly ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"who has been running the West Wing policy process on the issue ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"\" thinks","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Congress should ' ve gotten its act together a lot longer ago . \"","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Katie reported on Friday","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"that a decision was imminent ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"though the White House said","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"an official announcement is slated for Tuesday .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"Under DACA , there are around 800,000 illegal aliens","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"benefitting from the program","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"and they ' ve been preparing \" for the worst \"","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"( via USA Today ) :","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"We 're taking it day by day ,","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"because one day it 's one thing","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"and another day it 's another ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"but we must be prepared for the worst , ''","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"said Luz Gallegos , community programs director at TODEC Legal Center .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"`` We 're making sure the community has all their family plans in place ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"making sure","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"kids are aware ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"you know ,","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"if something were to happen to parents ,","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"what next steps to take . '' [ ... ]","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"Gary Finn , an Indio immigration attorney , said","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"the effects of a DACA repeal would not be immediate .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"Some people would lose their jobs","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"when their work permits expired , if not sooner .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"Immigration and Customs Enforcement could begin removal proceedings for DACA recipients ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"but that process takes years","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"`` People may go into a panic ,","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"I 'm kind of afraid of that ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"but it 's not like ICE will be knocking on the doors the next day , ''","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Finn said .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"Last week , Axios ' Jonathan Swan reported","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"that one of the reasons","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"why DACA was n the chopping block","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"was that the Trump administration ' s lawyers felt","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"that they could not defend its legality .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Moreover , Swan added","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"that even the Department of Homeland Security noted","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"if Congress wanted to keep DACA","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"as it is today ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"it would require an act of Congress .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"The constitutionality of this Obama-era executive action has been in legal limbo for years .","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"In short , the program allows illegal aliens","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"who entered the U.S. as minors","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"to be shielded from deportation , with the possibility of a work permit ,","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"if they meet certain criteria .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"The application fee is $ 495 .","depth":4},{"id":92,"text":"Donald Trump ran on a hardline immigration enforcement platform .","depth":2},{"id":93,"text":"It ' s looking like this will be another promise","depth":3},{"id":94,"text":"kept by Trump .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":189,"left":186,"right":188,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":144,"right":185,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":101,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":97,"right":100,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":96,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":6,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":98,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":128,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":106,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":102,"right":105,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":104,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":9,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":109,"right":126,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":13,"right":108,"relation":"purpose",